    "description":  "How employers can access recruitment APIs and API keys using their apprenticeship service account.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"what-do-our-apis-do\"\u003eWhat do our APIs do?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAPIs (Application Programming Interfaces) let applications share information and data with each other.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe have two APIs you can use:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eRecruitment API – our Recruitment API allows you to create adverts on Find an apprenticeship using your own systems\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eDisplay adverts API – our Display adverts API allows you to display adverts from Find an apprenticeship on your own websites\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-do-i-use-the-apis\"\u003eHow do I use the APIs?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"call-to-action\"\u003e\n  \u003cp\u003eYou’ll need someone with technical knowledge to connect your system with the API, for example a software developer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can share this \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://developer.apprenticeships.education.gov.uk/#employer-provider-api-info\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003edeveloper get started page\u003c/a\u003e with the person who is going to connect your system with the API, they can access the API from there.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou will need to give your developer API keys. The keys give your developer permission to connect to the API on your behalf.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYour developer will also be able able to try out the API using the sandbox provided.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"where-do-i-access-the-api-key\"\u003eWhere do I access the API Key?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you have owner permissions you will be able to access the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://api-management.manage-apprenticeships.service.gov.uk/subscriptions/api-list\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eAPI keys here\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
